    "description": "An engaging retro vibe arcade to relax and surpass your achievements with every game.<br>Pickup resources and use them to aquire physical and magical powers of your choice <br>to defeat opponents while avoiding obstacles and traps in your path.<br><br>Complement your play sessions with a suitable generated game environment, <br>lighting mood and ambient track of you liking to get the game rhythm going.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>INFINITE GAMEPLAY</strong></h2>Update includes new level allowing for procedural-infinite gameplay variations with each new game. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202070/extras/5f4bf5ad695823bf2d08f8d1d826b0bd.webp?t=1715545016\" width=616 height=58 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ITEMS</strong></h2>Use over 30 physical and magical items at your will to defeat your opponents.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202070/extras/11f9a8ac55839ed9c259c44970492591.avif?t=1715545016\" width=616 height=192 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ENEMY`s</strong></h2>Combat with over 15 types of enemy`s with different skills and abilities.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202070/extras/a8292c359056cc076bcbc737a437e8c6.avif?t=1715545016\" width=616 height=122 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TRAPS and OBSTACLES</strong></h2>Use your skills to avoid the many traps and obstacles in your path.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202070/extras/f9e4e05bcf59c59bdaab5107c6237ccd.avif?t=1715545016\" width=616 height=70 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RESOURCES</strong></h2>Collect and use resources at your disposal to achieve your goals. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202070/extras/8e14db57dbc8bef257e93a3c9fef9c89.avif?t=1715545016\" width=192 height=64 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MUSIC and MOOD</strong></h2>Choose a suiting sountrack and ambient mood to complement your play style.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202070/extras/0ef8009eb7d284e1ce250b3511b9d3cd.avif?t=1715545016\" width=616 height=92 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHALLENGES</strong></h2>Take on challenges and boast your highest scores.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202070/extras/b126b2ba0fe48589ef9e37bdea4911a1.avif?t=1715545016\" width=446 height=224 /></span>",
